31/03/2008
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- An Italian military delegation led by Chief of Staff of the Italian Air Force Lieutenant General Vincenzo Camporini visited BiH on Friday (March 28th) and met BiH counterpart General Sifet Podzic. 
After reviewing co-operation prospects, they agreed BiH officers could undergo training in Italy for peacekeeping activities. 
Italy also agreed to help with an English language proficiency test, which could prove helpful to NATO membership efforts. 
(Fena, RTRS - 28/03/08)
